http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Three-of-family-murdered/article13984457.ece

A family of three persons - a 14-year-old girl, her mother and grandfather - were found murdered at their house in Bhimegowdana Doddi in Ramanagaram on Wednesday. They have been identified as Sukanya, Gouramma (47) and Maregowda (60).The Harohalli police who rushed to the spot and are conducting a probe suspect that the girl might have raped by the assailant before being murdered. The reason for the triple murder is yet to be ascertained, police added.